{"tid":2506642,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"鹽, 雞粉, 味精 - 邊樣好?","createTime":"2021-04-27T12:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T15:49:20.000Z","uid":148023,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f477deb57351e1fd727e50ba56810a4485481b11","tid":2506642,"uid":148023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:22:01.000Z","msg":"如果用鈉嚟睇<br />\n每1g...<br />\n鹽有400mg鈉 &gt; 雞粉170mg鈉 &gt;味精112mg鈉<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbiJVoUPKP5C9LBKBjG5EJogmjQ1GtNdKGhNzs991LPUB?filename=FQODVBV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFQODVBV.png&h=b6058b56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQMLQpa3P47QFELRzL2LQRbjb4i2HZAyhthS4oBgM6531?filename=vMocZ3D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvMocZ3D.png&h=47829021&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbVBESHrZ923LZL811RdwvmwoKCwsHkzraNryqHvewDL3?filename=X5EGToH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5EGToH.png&h=b8c94ac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣睇應該係味精比其他2項健康<br />\n<br />\n到睇成份, 鹽 應該係最天然<br />\n其次係味精(由海藻/甜菜/蔗/麥糖萃取出麩氨酸鈉)<br />\n雞粉個成份仲複雜有(鹽, 麥芽糖糊糊, E621同E635即係味精, 仲有栗粉....)<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇應該係味精&gt;鹽=雞粉?<br />\n<br />\nPs.當然就乜柒都唔落最健康, 但下下白烚西蘭花真係頂唔順。<br />\n另外當然仲有好多調味料, 都歡迎大家提出, 有錯亦都請大家指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f169bfe7c08acf692fe66a014b728f7b828be8","tid":2506642,"uid":148023,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77824538f184bd559c107580fcfa239ad0c1340","tid":2506642,"uid":118754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"落雞汁"}]}